@startuml
' Scope: logical components and dependency direction
' Related: NFR-SEC-01, NFR-SEC-02, NFR-REL-01
title katekyo コンポーネント図

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor Teacher
actor Student
actor Parent

package "Next.js application" {
  [Server Components\npage.tsx / layout.tsx] as Pages
  [Client Components\nforms / charts / interactions] as Clients
  [Server Actions\nactions.ts] as Actions
  [Route Handlers\napp/api/**/route.ts] as Routes
  [Authentication & guards\nNextAuth / action-guards] as Auth
  [Domain helpers\nbilling / garden / validation] as Domain
  [Prisma data access] as Data
  [External adapters\nLINE / QStash / Storage] as Adapters
}

database "PostgreSQL" as DB
cloud "LINE Messaging API" as LINE
cloud "Upstash QStash" as QSTASH
cloud "Supabase Storage" as STORAGE

Teacher --> Pages
Student --> Pages
Parent --> Pages
Pages --> Clients : serializable props
Pages --> Auth
Pages --> Data : server-side query
Clients --> Actions : form / transition
Actions --> Auth : session + role
Actions --> Domain
Actions --> Data : tenant-scoped query
Actions --> Adapters : best-effort notification
Routes --> Auth : session / bearer / signature
Routes --> Domain
Routes --> Data : scoped query
Routes --> Adapters
Data --> DB
Adapters --> LINE
Adapters --> QSTASH
Adapters --> STORAGE

note right of Auth
  UIの表示制御は認可境界ではない。
  書き込み前にサーバー側で
  actorと対象リソースを検証する。
end note
@enduml

